  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travellin Cats in Germany (formerly Cats Hidden in Germany) is a cute hidden object game set in medieval Germany. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 cats are waiting for you to be discovered within a hand-drawn background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax thanks to the chill soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Found a cat? Click on it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 1 Level, 100 cats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❔ Easter Eggs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 Hint System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏰ Timer mode with leaderboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚙️ In-game Settings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776570/extras/bfb6752cab8c9773011c7ceb72c21a8e.webp?t=1772094915\" width=600 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776570/extras/ae91cfca28b4fb2430ae97f744716f86.avif?t=1772094915\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776570/extras_big/ae91cfca28b4fb2430ae97f744716f86.avif?t=1772094915 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
